and Vespers each of the parishes and missions of the
Archdiocese of Seattle on a Sunday near their feast day</i>. This
week we remember in prayer the parish of St. Mary
Magdalene in Everett, and the nuns of the Carmelite
Monastery of St. Joseph in Shoreline.</p>
 
